                   SUBJECTS* NEEDED FOR COGNITIVE STUDIES

   wavyln.gif

     [stripe.jpg]


   The Laboratory of Brain and Cognition is recruiting research volunteers
   for cognitive and brain imaging studies of learning, memory and
   attention. Subjects should be healthy, have good vision and be aged
   20-40. Studies occur throughout the year.

   For more information, call:


